node.text:
We're loving @anamaria's sight of the Adriatic Sea in Hvar Island, Croatia's Adriatic Sea nook that's sought-after by even the most exquisite travelers. 🏝

Hvar, a Croatian island in the Adriatic Sea, is best known as a summer resort. Highlights of the port town Hvar include its 13th-century walls, a hilltop fortress and a main square anchored by the Renaissance-era Hvar Cathedral. The island also features beaches such as Dubovica and inland lavender fields. Boat excursions serve the nearby Pakleni Islands, which have secluded beaches and coves.✨

Have you heard of this island and have you ever been to Croatia? 🇭🇷

📽 @anamaria
📍 Hvar Island, Croatia
🎶 will.i.am - Good Morning

node.text:
He can kick you out of Australia 🥊

📽 @jayprehistoricpets

The red kangaroo is the largest of all kangaroos, the largest terrestrial mammal native to Australia, and the largest extant marsupial. It is found across mainland Australia, except for the more fertile areas, such as southern Western Australia, the eastern and southeastern coasts, and the rainforests along the northern coast.

node.text:
Alaskan adventures with @johnderting 💦
From 1-10, which one is your favorite?

📽 @johnderting
📍 Alaska
🎶 
1. (River sounds) - (Relaxing Radiance Music For Sleep
2, 4. Lovely - Billie Eilish and Khalid
3, 5. Rose - James Horner
6. Rainy Day - Peder B. Helland
7. The Night We Met - Lord Huron
8. What the Hell - Williams
9. Six Feet Under - Billie Eilish
10. Hymn To The Sea - Sarah Cothran & Michaila Cothran

node.text:
Umbrella tree 🌳 How impressive is this holm oak? Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📽 @brigrc
📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy
